<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/23164911-the-fateful-lightning"><img alt="The Fateful Lightning (Civil War: 1861-1865, Western Theater, #4)" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1411333818l/23164911._SY75_.jpg" />
